These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, blueberry, apricot, orange, cranberry
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, metal, dubstep, jazz, country
1. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
4. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating orange##1
5. the person eating cabbage is between the fan of jazz and the fan of dubstep##2
6. the person eating cranberry is in the middle##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
8. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | blueberry | cabbage | cranberry | orange | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | country      | jazz   | indie     | metal    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite, cola
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, biathlon, skiing, soccer, rowing
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | sprite       | cola    | hot-chocolate | mirinda   |
| Sport      | biathlon | rugby | soccer | rowing      | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: traveling, camping, writing, photography, skydiving
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, disco, punk, rock, ambient
1. the fan of rock is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
5. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
6. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | traveling | writing | camping | photography    | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | pop        | punk      | disco | ambient      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, card-games, skydiving, fishing, photography
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, fantasy, zombie, epic, musical
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in the middle##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's hobby is photography##2
7. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking      | fishing | skydiving | card-games   | photography  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | musical    | zombie        | time-travel | fantasy |

