.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, water, fanta, milk
There are 5 different nationalities: american, chinese, colombian, indonesian, thai
1. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the american##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the thai##1
4. the colombian is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
5. the thai is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the chinese is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | milk      | almond-milk | coffee   | fanta  | water  |
| Nationality   | colombian | indonesian | american | chinese | thai |

