.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, coffee, milk, iced-tea
The people have 5 different jobs:  nurse, freelancer, entrepreneur, librarian, chef
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
2. the freelancer is between the chef and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the freelancer##1
5. the entrepreneur is the person drinking coffee##1
6. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
8. the librarian is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | sprite        | juice                | milk  | coffee  | iced-tea            |
| Job        | nurse | chef | freelancer | entrepreneur | librarian |

