The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, epic, adventure, fantasy, horror
1. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching horror movies##2
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
