.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, german, pakistani, australian, nigerian
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, rabbit, ferret, turtle
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
2. the australian is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the australian##1
4. the australian is on the far right##1
5. the german is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the pakistani is between the german and the russian##2
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the pakistani##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | german | pakistani     | russian | australian |
| Pet           | chinchilla | hedgehog     | rabbit | turtle    | ferret      |

