3. the person who's sport is rugby is the architect##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the architect##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
6. the pilot is on the left of the photographer##1
7. the designer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | pilot | photographer | designer | architect | journalist |
| Sport   | badminton | skateboarding | volleyball    | rugby    | surfing  |

