.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
There 5 different types of food: zucchini, carrot, raspberry, orange, apricot
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, cycling, sailing, snowboarding
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the person eating zucchini is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is soccer##2
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating carrot is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | carrot    | apricot  | zucchini      | orange     | raspberry |
| Sport   | lacrosse | soccer | sailing | cycling | snowboarding |

