.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
There 5 different types of food: pear, grapes, eggplant, cauliflower, corn
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, scooter, train, tram
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the tram is the person eating pear##1
3. the person driving the tram is in the middle##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the tram and the person eating grapes##2
7. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Food        | cauliflower | corn | pear  | eggplant | grapes     |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | scooter     | tram | helicopter      | train |

