.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, trance, classical, ambient, folk
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, boat, jet-ski, subway, motorbike
1. the fan of ambient is the person driving the boat##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is between the fan of trance and the person driving the bike##2
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | ambient | classical     | folk     | trance |
| Transport     | subway   | boat   | bike | jet-ski | motorbike  |

