.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, mystery, musical, western, comedy
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, ship, bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
9. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | mystery | comedy     | musical | western |
| Transport     | bike       | subway   | ship | snowmobile   | motorbike        |

