.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, metal, electronic, jazz, d&b
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, roller, scooter, ship, bike
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the ship##2
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the bike is the fan of funk##1
7. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | electronic      | jazz | d&b     | metal      |
| Transport     | bike | roller | ship | bus | scooter |

 